text: "Grace" is a 1994 debut single by Jeff Buckley and is the title track from his debut studio album Grace. It went to number 91 in Australia. ==Track listing== #"Grace" #"Tongue" #"Kanga-Roo" #"Grace" ==Track listing Australian single== #"Grace" #"Grace (live)" #"Mojo Pin (live)" #"Hallelujah (live)" ==References== Category:1994 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Jeff Buckley songs Category:Alternative rock songs Category:Psychedelic rock songs Category:Celtic rock songs
